sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staf
    participant Sistem
    participant Basis Data
    participant Chatbot

    Staf->>Sistem: Lihat riwayat pengingat
    activate Sistem
    Sistem->>Basis Data: Query log pengingat terkirim
    activate Basis Data
    Basis Data-->>Sistem: Data riwayat
    deactivate Basis Data
    Sistem-->>Staf: Daftar log pengingat
    deactivate Sistem
    
    Staf->>Sistem: Kirim pengingat manual
    activate Sistem
    Sistem->>Chatbot: Request kirim pesan WA
    activate Chatbot
    Chatbot-->>Sistem: Sukses
    deactivate Chatbot
    Sistem->>Basis Data: Simpan log pengiriman baru
    activate Basis Data
    Basis Data-->>Sistem: Terupdate
    deactivate Basis Data
    Sistem-->>Staf: Notifikasi berhasil terkirim
    deactivate Sistem